aVAnd so I decided to actually talk about race.
p79
aVAnd I decided that if I came here and shared with you
p80
aVsome of my experiences,
p81
aVthat maybe we could all be a little less anxious
p82
aVand a little more bold
p83
aVin our conversations about race.
