aVand I said, "Why are we doing breath-holding exercises?"
p183
aVAnd my coach looked me at me, and he said, "Mellody,
p184
aVthat was not a breath-holding exercise.
p185
aVThat drill was to make you comfortable
p186
aVbeing uncomfortable,
