aa(lp213
VNow, my favorite example of color bravery
p214
aVis a guy named John Skipper.
p215
aVHe runs ESPN.
p216
aVHe's a North Carolina native,
p217
aVquintessential Southern gentleman, white.
p218
aVHe joined ESPN, which already had a culture
p219
aVof inclusion and diversity, but he took it up a notch.
p220
aVHe demanded that every open position
p221
aVhave a diverse slate of candidates.
