aVIf you're part of a hiring process
p263
aVor an admissions process,
p264
aVyou can be color brave.
p265
aVIf you are trying to solve a really hard problem,
p266
aVyou can speak up and be color brave.
p267
aVNow I know people will say,
p268
aVbut that doesn't add up to a lot,
p269
aVbut I'm actually asking you to do something really simple:
p270
aVobserve your environment,
p271
aVat work, at school, at home.
p272
aVI'm asking you to look at the people around you
p273
aVpurposefully and intentionally.
